result.execSummary:
The defendant Dirk Robert McCall was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Dirk Robert McCall is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Dirk Robert McCall was found guilty of Possession of THC (2nd+ Offense), a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
